HTTP-Validate

A Perl module to validate and clean HTTP request parameter values according to a set of rules

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc HTTP::Validate

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        https://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=HTTP-Validate

    MetaCPAN:
        https://metacpan.org/search?q=HTTP%3A%3AValidate


